\id PHM  
\h FILIMON 
\toc1 Filimon 
\toc2 Flm 
\mt1 Filimon  
\mt2 N…ôkw…ôkw…ô yame Pol r…®m…®rai k…®mi Filimon  
\imt1 N…ôgkiarien kup…ôn ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e Filimon  
\ip \bd ?Pa r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e? \bd* Aposol Pol r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e.  
\ip \bd ?R…®m…®rai ramv…ôn k…®mi pa?\bd* R…®m…®rai ramv…ôn k…®mi Filimon ye nim…ôhuak apa Kolosi. Iriu fren huv…ô. Filimon, kafan aik…®n slef m…®n…ô.  
\ip \bd ?Nar…ôyen r…®mnhawor p…ôn iran m…®ne ye n…®p…®g r…®m…®rai?\bd* Ye n…®p…®g a, narmam…ô khapsaah, kap…ôri…ô aik…®n slef m…®n…ô. K…®ni n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô m…®n t…®ks…®n, kap…ôri…ô aik…®n slef m…®n…ô. Filimon, kafan k…®rik aik…®n slef, nhag…®n e Onesimas. M…ôr…®g Onesimas r…®mn…ôkr…ôh k…®n mane t…®ks…®n kape Filimon, map. Tukm…ô Filimon r…ôm Onesimas, loa kape Rom ramni m…ô Filimon r…®rkun nhopniyen in tukun. M…ôr…®g Onesimas rap, m…®v…ôn, m…ôm Pol ye kalabus apa Rom, k…®ni Pol ramni-…ôrhav N…ôvsaoyen Huv…ô k…®min, in ramni n…ôfrak…®sien ye Yesu Kristo. K…®ni mamasitu m…®n ye Pol. K…®ni Pol rher-p…ôn k…®n in r…®rer…®g p…ôn tuk Filimon. Pol ramni p…ôn tuk Filimon m…ô nar apnap…®g m…ô Onesimas in slef kafan, m…ôr…®g takt…ôkun ai, in ruau…ô r…ômhen k…®n piauni, meinai iriu kwis k…®r…ôni n…ôfrak…®sien ye Yesu Kristo.  
\ip \bd ?R…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e tuk naha?\bd* Pol r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e maiyoh Filimon m…ô tukr…ôru-k…®n norien has kape Onesimas, k…®ni m…®v…ôh in ramrer…®g-p…ô m…®n. Nar apnap…®g m…ô in slef kafan, m…ôr…®g Pol rorkeikei m…ô Filimon tukr…ôm huv…ô Onesimas r…ômhen k…®n piauni k…®rik.  
\c 1  
\s1 Pol r…®m…ô n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e, ramv…ôn k…®mi Filimon  
\pi1
\v 1 Filimon. Yo Pol, yame k…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn yo ye kalabus tuk n…®ni-…ôrhavyen Yesu Kristo, k…®mru piautaw…ô Timoti, yakar…ôrai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e k…®mik.  
\pi1 Filimon, ik k…®mru k…®rik, k…®ni k…®tas…®r karhor wok k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô kape Kughen.  
\v 2 K…®ni yakar…ôrai m…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e k…®mi nowintaw…ô e Apia, m…®ne kw…ôn e Akipas, yame k…®taw…ô min, k…®s…ômhen k…®n mobael m…®n…ô kape kwhen k…®rikian…ô. K…®ni yakarani rhuv…ô k…®mi n…ômhuak yam…ô m…®ne khau…ô m…®s…ôhuak ye kafam nim…ô.\x - \xo 1:2 \xt Kol 4:17; 2 Tim 2:3 \x*   
\pi1
\v 3 P…ôh Kughen, R…®mtaw…ô, m…®ne Yesu Kristo Yermaru kap…ôtaw…ô, iriu tukraw…ôhsi-pre n…®huv…ôyen, m…®ne norkeikeiyen k…®mi …ômi…ô.   
\s1 Norien huv…ô kape Filimon  
\p
\v 4 Filimon. N…®p…®g yakam…ôhuak, n…®p…®g fam, r…®kik ram…ôs…®k ik, mamni vi vi Kughen  
\v 5 meinai yakam…ôr…®g n…ôvsaoyen k…®n nhat…ôt…ôyen kafam ye Yesu Yermaru, m…®ne norkeikeiyen kafam tuk n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô.  
\v 6 Yakamaiyoh Kughen m…ô k…®mi…ô narmam…ô t…®ks…®n yam…ô m…®ne naksar…ô mas…ôhuak kwis, takhau…ô mharkun n…®huv…ôyen yam…ô m…®ne kamhas…®-p…ôn tuk Yesu Kristo.  
\v 7 Piak, yakamni vi vi Kughen meinai kafam norkeikeiyen ramor n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô kas…ôr…®g rhuv…ô. Norien kafam rav…ôhsi hakt…ô kafak n…ôr…®gien, r…®kik ragien.\x - \xo 1:7 \xt 2 Kor 7:4 \x*   
\s1 Pol ramarkut k…®mi Filimon m…ô tukr…®p…ôh n…®v…ôhsi-p…ônien narp…®nien k…®mi Onesimas, meighaan k…®n in r…®rer…®g-p…ô m…®n  
\p
\v 8 Ye nhag Yesu Kristo, yak…®rkun narkutien k…®mik m…ô takor nar k…®rik yame takam…ôkeikei mamor. M…ôr…®g, to yakp…ôh narkutien k…®mik. Yakam…ôm norkeikeiyen kafam  
\v 9 mamaiyoh ik m…ô takor nar k…®rik ye n…®kar…®n kape norkeikeiyen. Ror m…ôkneik…®n m…ô yo Pol, yo huaru k…®rik, k…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn yo ye kalabus tuk n…®niyen nhag Yesu Kristo,  
\v 10 yakamaiyoh ik ye n…®kar…®n kape slef kafam, nhag…®n e Onesimas\f + \fr 1:10 \ft  Nhag e Onesimas, n…®pran r…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYermam…ô yame r…®rkun huv…ô norien wok.‚Äù\f*.\x - \xo 1:10 \xt 1 Kor 4:15; Kol 4:9 \x* Kw…ôn en r…®mau…ô r…ômhen k…®n nar…®k n…®p…®g y…®mnamar…ô ye kalabus.  
\v 11 Apa kup…ôn, in r…®m…®p…ôh nor-huv…ôyen wok kafam, m…ôr…®g takt…ôkun ai, in r…®mau…ô m…®rkun nor-huv…ôyen wok kap…ôrao.   
\p
\v 12 K…®ni takt…ôkun ai, yakamher-pre k…®n kw…ôn e, yame yakorkeikei p…®k in.  
\v 13 Yakm…ô jakor in ramar…ô …ôm…ô k…®mru min, p…ôh tukr…®v…ôh tamhek…®m, mamasitu irak ye n…®p…®g yakamar…ô ye kalabus tuk n…®niyen N…ôgkiarien Huv…ô kape Kughen.  
\v 14 M…ôr…®g, to yakp…ôh norien nar k…®rik m…ôkup…ôn kik tukm…ô nakp…ôh neighanien k…®n.   
\p
\v 15 Yakeinein, tukm…ô ror Onesimas r…®mnap ta iram tuk n…®p…®g kwakw…ô e m…ô takv…ôh m…®n in r…®rer…®g-pre m…®n nakawar…ô apomh.  
\v 16 M…ôr…®g p…ôh nien m…ô in tukror …ôm…ô slef kafam, n…®kam. M…ôr…®g takt…ôkun ai, in slef, m…ôr…®g ruau…ô kw…ôn k…®rik rhuv…ô p…®k rapita slef k…®rik, in ruau…ô piaurao yame kworkeikei p…®k in. Yakorkeikei in, m…ôr…®g ik nakorkeikei p…®k in rapita, meinai in kafam slef, k…®ni ye nhag Yesu Yermaru, piam.\x - \xo 1:16 \xt 1 Tim 6:2 \x*   
\p
\v 17 Filimon, yakam…ôm m…ô k…®rau k…®rau…ô k…®rikian…ô, k…®ni ror m…ôkneik…®n, yakamaiyoh ik m…ô tukm…ô Onesimas rur…ô, takamor …ôm…ô ramhuv…ô p…ôn k…®min r…ômhen k…®n yame nakamor huv…ô-p…ô k…®mi yo.  
\v 18 M…ôr…®g tukm…ô r…®mnor nar k…®rik rahah iram, u…ô r…®m…®v…ôh kafam k…®rik nar k…®rik m…®p…ôh n…ôrokien, tak…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn ram…ôm…®r ye kaon kafak.  
\v 19 K…®ni ai takt…ôkun, yo Pol, yakamrai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e k…®n kwerm…®k, p…ôh yo jakpi…ôrok ik. ?M…ôr…®g nakm…ô jak…ôrok ik u…ô? Takp…ôh n…ôru-k…®nien m…ô yo y…®mnasitu iram k…®ni n…®m…®v…ôh kafam n…®mraghien rer…®n. Rap…ôh n…ômhenien m…ô takuh r…®kik m…ô jak…ôrok ik tuk nar k…®rik.  
\v 20 Piak, yakm…ô takor nar e yame yakamaiyoh ik k…®n ye nhag Yesu Yermaru, in e takor r…®kik tukram…ôr…®g rhuv…ô ye Yesu Kristo.  
\v 21 Yakamrai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e k…®mik meinai yak…®rkun m…ô takor n…ôkwak, k…®ni takamor tukrapita naha nhag…®n yame yakamaiyoh k…®n.   
\p
\v 22 K…®ni nar k…®rik m…®n, takamor apn…ôpen…ô ye kw…ônmhan k…®rik kafak, meinai yakam…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn kafak n…ôt…ôr…®gien ye Kughen m…ô in tukror swatuk k…®mi yo jakrer…®g-pre m…®n tuk …ômi…ô r…ômhen k…®n yame k…®mi…ô n…®m…®s…ôhuak tukun.\x - \xo 1:22 \xt Fil 1:25; 2:24 \x*   
\s1 N…ôgkiarien infamien  
\p
\v 23 Kw…ôn e Epafras, k…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn …ômru ye kalabus tuk n…®ni-…ôrhavyen nhag Yesu Kristo, k…®ni in ramni-pre rhuv…ô tuk ik.\x - \xo 1:23 \xt Kol 1:7 \x*  
\v 24 K…®ni Mak, m…®ne Aristakas, m…®ne Demas, m…®ne Luk, yam…ô m…®ne k…®maw…ô yaksor wok k…®rikian…ô, iri…ô m…®n kamhani-pre rhuv…ô tuk ik.\x - \xo 1:24 \xt Kol 4:10-14 \x*   
\p
\v 25 P…ôh n…®huv…ôyen kape Kughen tukramar…ô tuk …ômi…ô m-fam.   